Python Operators

Categories: arithmetic (+ - * / // % **), assignment (= += ...),
comparison (== != < > <= >=), logical (and or not),
identity (is, is not), membership (in, not in), bitwise (& | ^ ~ << >>).

Operator precedence: parentheses first; ** before unary + -; then * / // %; then + -; etc.

See also: https://www.w3schools.com/python/python_operators.asp
